text: Hi everyone. I just joined. I am in Ethiopia and have a high tech lab "blueLab" with a team and several 3d printers and iot devices. We are trying to create prototypes of 3D printed equipment that can help with self protection and  assist hospitals by 3D printing small equipment that are scarce in the market.

<@UV8B0679P>   <@UV83NPH0T> 

In Rwanda , The Ministry of Health built a tool  that respond questions from people who are asking using SMS automatically.  They kinda built a AI feature that understand the question and respond to users and they are using Africa's Talking SMS API as two way SMS gatway. The same API  is already integrated now with the platform we are building in Ethiopia for Bulk SMS. So I was thinking If any one can do or try build the AI thing that can understand people question and prepare an answer, it might be worth exploring and can ease the pressure on the call centers.
